1.0.name: wordpress/youlicit-more-widget
1.0.description:
The Youlicit More plugin will automatically look at links on your blog and provide your readers will additional information from the most recommended sites on the web. Effortlessly give your readers more relevant content to your topic of conversation. Learn more at http://www.youlicit.com

In addition, request an invitation to the "Featured Blogs program" and promote your blog on Youlicit to people interested in the topics you blog about! To learn more visit http://www.youlicit.com/help/featured_blog.aspx

Note: This widget is currently in beta. To stay updated with the latest news see http://blog.youlicit.com and sign up for the Featured Blog program!
